title: Web CEO + Crack
description:
Web CEO is a suite of search engine marketing tools in one software program, including a keyword generator, web page optimization analyzer, auto and manual submitter, ranking monitor, top-ranked web page analyzer, HTML editor, FTP client, and traffic counter and analyzer.

Keywords generates up to 1,000 keyword phrases - including daily search count - that&#039;s related to the keyword you enter, per search query. 
Search Engine Optimization analyzes your web page and compares important ranking elements with top 10 ranked pages in major search engines, to find out how to improve your rankings. 
Auto Submission automatically submits your web pages to top search engines with one click. 
Manual Submission gives one-click access to search engines and web directories that require manual or paid submissions, in addition to pay per click search engines. 
Ranking checks your web page rankings in dozens of major search engines and web directories worldwide. 
Auditor analyzes your web site for errors and broken links. 
Editor lets you access, view and edit the elements of your HTML page using a simple WYSIWYG (What You See Is What You Get) editor. 
Uploader is a FTP client, which lets you upload your optimized pages to your server. 
HitLens is a traffic counting and analysis program that allows you to view and analyze traffic visiting your Web site. This is an optional service that requires a monthly subscription fee. 
Search engine data is updated every 1-3 days. 
 
 
Benefits: Saves time by automating repetitive tasks, such as automatically filling in your page title, meta description, and meta keywords tag into the corresponding fields of a search engine&#039;s submission form, for every page of your site. 
Submits web pages to search engines in a non-spam manner by following each search engine&#039;s submission guidelines to prevent accidental spamming. 
Shows you exactly how your web pages rank in the top search engines. 
Gives you insight into the elements of your web pages that could be changed to improve your search search engine rankings. 
Shows you what keywords you should target and include in your web pages. 
Helps you ensure your web pages are error free. 
Includes a FTP client, so need to fork out additional money for one. 
Up-to-date search engine data ensures error-free submissions and ranking results. 
BE KIND TO OTHERS. PLEASE SEED!!
